ar about it. And if you are worried about the solvency of your bank, you ca=
n tweet or Whatsapp or group-text about it, and worries can spread faster, =
and you can withdraw your money via app. =E2=80=9CGame=E2=80=99s the same, =
just got more fierce,=E2=80=9D is the diagnosis of the vice chairman of the=
