I assume the investigation is less about =E2=80=9Cdid you mess up the capit=
al raise=E2=80=9D and more about =E2=80=9Cdid you buy the bond portfolio at=
 a price that was good for you and made the capital situation worse,=E2=80=
=9D but the capital raise did not help.=C2=A0
