<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Toronto-Dominion Bank and First Horizon Corp. =
have agreed to terminate their previously announced merger amid uncertainty=
 about the possibility of regulatory approvals.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The lenders said in a statement Thursday that =
they =E2=80=9Centered into a mutual agreement=E2=80=9D to terminate their 2=
